<section class="split">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Setup Required</p>
    <h1>Connect Supabase to run Getsustho</h1>
    <p>The Node app is ready, but it needs Supabase credentials in <code>.env</code> before it can read or write hospital data.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Required values</h2>
    <pre>SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=</pre>
    <p>Run the SQL file in <code>supabase/migrations</code>, then restart the server.</p>
  </div>
</section>
